casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Michael Anthony TERRELL, Jr., Defendant-Appellant. SC: 159307
COA: 345619 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the January 23, 2019 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because the defendant has failed to meet the burden of establishing entitlement to relief under MCR 6.508(D).
